cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically in the area of autonomous vehicles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning), and tracking algorithms, which fall under cs.RO (Robotics). Additionally, the paper involves data association, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and the use of a state-of-the-art filter, which falls under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
